  "3337350": {
    "name": "FYR: The Lost Island",
    "steam_appid": 3337350,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras/d870bbc69f9a808d22e7b016af2e0d13.avif?t=1771446210\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras_big/d870bbc69f9a808d22e7b016af2e0d13.avif?t=1771446210 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上杳无人迹的海岸，这是一处为神秘笼罩、被遗忘的过去萦绕的挪威荒岛。该岛曾拥有一个繁荣的渔业社区，如今却沉寂在阴森恐怖之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你探索这座废弃岛屿的过程中，每一条线索、每一张纸条、每一处隐藏的遗迹都会揭开更多黑暗历史的面纱。从黑暗的灯塔到废弃的房屋，每个角落都隐藏着这里曾经繁荣的生活片段——在一切都变成废墟之前。是什么黑暗力量打破了岛上居民的生活？你能抵挡住黑暗的侵袭，找到在其深处等待的答案吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras/b2382ab135dcb3d2c64017d3bc85ef7d.avif?t=1771446210\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras_big/b2382ab135dcb3d2c64017d3bc85ef7d.avif?t=1771446210 width=800 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras/5a6875236506e2ef0d67479421a9754c.poster.avif?t=1771446210\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras/5a6875236506e2ef0d67479421a9754c.webm?t=1771446210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras/5a6875236506e2ef0d67479421a9754c.mp4?t=1771446210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>你并不孤单。一个无情的怪物在阴影中追逐着你，每一声吱吱嘎嘎的低语，彷佛都在提醒着它的存在，它会在你最意想不到的时候逼近你。你没有武器保护自己，必须用智慧躲避它的魔爪。这种生物会被光线和声音吸引，你在揭开探索小岛秘密的过程中不得不小心翼翼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras/c4b323a53477b691f5e22501b128e5c9.avif?t=1771446210\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras_big/c4b323a53477b691f5e22501b128e5c9.avif?t=1771446210 width=800 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras/d3ce8d53f87651d4cb81b70eef6f80d9.poster.avif?t=1771446210\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras/d3ce8d53f87651d4cb81b70eef6f80d9.webm?t=1771446210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras/d3ce8d53f87651d4cb81b70eef6f80d9.mp4?t=1771446210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>阴森恐怖的岛上氛围与身临其境的VR技术相结合，创造出一种直观的恐怖体验，让您身临其境地感受恐怖氛围。当您在动态环境中穿梭时，每一声嘎吱声、每一个阴影和每一个令人不寒而栗的细节都会让您感到恐惧。每一次互动都在模糊现实与噩梦之间的界限，让您完全融入这个令人毛骨悚然的美丽世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras/3d5a76e04f0ed77ecca6a8334da2e1c9.avif?t=1771446210\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras_big/3d5a76e04f0ed77ecca6a8334da2e1c9.avif?t=1771446210 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras/0ef7c996502b15959669e400f9e14a34.poster.avif?t=1771446210\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras/0ef7c996502b15959669e400f9e14a34.webm?t=1771446210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras/0ef7c996502b15959669e400f9e14a34.mp4?t=1771446210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>黑暗无边无际，光明是宝贵而脆弱的。在探索的过程中，光线会帮助你发现隐藏的线索，在复杂的环境中穿梭，并避开追捕你的生物。但要注意的是，肆意使用光线可能会引起不必要的注意。在照明和安全之间把握平衡，对你的生存至关重要。在游戏中，照明既可以帮助探索，又有暴露踪迹的风险，始终让玩家处在一种动态的压力之下，提醒人们在这个世界上，即使是光也可能是一把双刃剑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras/d3b309ae2c5130e901ac75c64c799652.avif?t=1771446210\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras_big/d3b309ae2c5130e901ac75c64c799652.avif?t=1771446210 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras/51ae5a3aaccc48c538dab70790cb9409.poster.avif?t=1771446210\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras/51ae5a3aaccc48c538dab70790cb9409.webm?t=1771446210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337350/extras/51ae5a3aaccc48c538dab70790cb9409.mp4?t=1771446210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>用光线揭示这座岛屿不为人知的历史，重新聆听那些消失的生活和挣扎。每一次闪烁都会揭开这座岛屿悲惨故事的片段，吸引你深入这座岛屿的奥秘，推动你接近真相。闪耀你的光芒，直面黑暗，拼凑被时间遗忘的秘密。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 挪威语, 乌克兰语, 波兰语, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 韩语, 简体中文, 繁体中文<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
